		<title>马云对中小企业管理的一些看法</title>
		<link>https://laputancn.wordpress.com/2008/03/07/%e9%a9%ac%e4%ba%91%e5%af%b9%e4%b8%ad%e5%b0%8f%e4%bc%81%e4%b8%9a%e7%ae%a1%e7%90%86%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%9b%e7%9c%8b%e6%b3%95/</link>
